DESCRIPTION:

NEW YORK SIEGE 
The phoenix terrorist cell has taken control of the DSB Computer Solutions building in downtown New York.There are a suspected number of 4 hostages being held in the conference room situated in the south building.

Terrorists: Prevent the oncoming counter-terrorist assault by all means necessary; do not let the hostages escape.

Counter-Terrorists: Rescue all 4 hostages and take out all enemies. Proceed with extreme caution.
